{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1a48b848b0","title":"关于修改宪法等问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"259d491817","index":0,"year":1970,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"1a48b848b0"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[{"id":"688be0d586","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"1a48b848b0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在周思来1970年3月17日给毛泽东等的报告上。报告说，3月16日的中央政治局会议进行了两项工作。“第一项讨论和通过了关子修改宪法问题的请示及其附件，现呈上请主席审阅后予以批示，以便着手修改。第二项通过了各省、市、自治区和各大军区、各总部、各军兵种来京协商四届人大代表名额和选举问题的负贵人名单。"}],"contents":[{"id":"be536dae6f","type":"title","text":"关于修改宪法等问题的批语叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"1a48b848b0"},{"id":"688be0d586","type":"paragraph","text":"同意第一项所提修改问题的意见。同时请各地方提修改意见附件留阅。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"1a48b848b0"}],"page":{"id":"a08a917513","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"1a48b848b0","start":523,"end":523}}}},"__N_SSG":true}